/span>在静坐过程中，<span class="_ _9"></span>或许会领悟到一</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y38 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">些平时觉察不到的真理。 </div><div class="t m0 x9 hd y9d ffc fs3 fc0 sc1 ls16 ws0">6.减轻压力 </div><div class="t m0 x1b h4 y9e ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">长期处于重负下，<span class="_ _9"></span>对人的身心极为不利。<span class="_ _9"></span>如果我们有禅</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y9f ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">修的习惯，就可以有效地纾缓压力。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
